snippet.title: Dungeons and Dragons Fangame Trailer
snippet.description:
A great trailer made by  BloodCrisis (bloodcrisis@gmail.com) showing some of game progress so far, Thanks man.

Release date? Soon :)

• *A segment of a metal cover from youtube user "ansgaros".https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=jhyfPp6bo8s&ab_channel=ShinobiSakriShinobiSakri
• *Some artwork is from a deviant user "jukuri96" https://www.deviantart.com/jkuri96

#DnD #Openbor #Fangame
